-- LLM solves, hard cell verifies (proof-carrying computation)

cell problem
  yield equation = 3x + 7 = 22

cell solve
  given problem.equation
  yield x
  ---
  Solve the equation «equation» for x. Output ONLY the numeric value, nothing else.
  ---

cell verify
  given solve.x
  yield check
  ---
  sql: SELECT CASE WHEN CAST(y.value_text AS DECIMAL) * 3 + 7 = 22 THEN 'PASS' ELSE 'FAIL' END FROM yields y JOIN cells c ON y.cell_id = c.id WHERE c.program_id = 'math-verify' AND c.name = 'solve' AND y.field_name = 'x' AND y.is_frozen = 1
  ---

cell explain
  given solve.x
  given verify.check
  yield summary
  ---
  The equation was «equation». The LLM solved x = «x». Verification result: «check». Write a one-sentence explanation.
  ---
